    "objective": "“to estimate population based pharmacokinetic of valproic acid (VPA) and to determine the effect of treatment and additional disease on its performance in children with epilepsy” AND “to describe the pharmacokinetic of valproic acid in a population of epileptic children using bayesian program of analysis.”",
    "covariates": "Tested: WT, AGE, Comedication (CBZ, DHP, PHB), additional disease. Included: WT, AGE",
    "observations": "The final model has a higher predictive performance in prediction of the serum concentration than the basic model. The estimates were significantly affected by weight, age, CBZ and gastroesophageal reflux (GER). But only age and weight are included in the model. A relationship is observed between observed and predicted plasma VPA concentration, which is poor at high concentrations.",
